      "role": "user",
      "content": "tea doesn't do anything. it's just more acting. even when i'm alone, i'm just waiting for the next thing to happen. if the 'me' part is already gone... then what am i even doing this for? it just feels like im taking up space for someone who isnt even there anymore.",
